channel.title: Port Forwarding
channel.description: I'm using portforward.com and it says i need to do this: We need to have the correct Name Server IP addresses. If we do not, you will not be able to browse the web. There are a couple ways to get these. The first way is to log into your router's web interface, and look at your router's status page. where can i find the status page for a NETGEAR DG834G?
